WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.000 --> 00:00:02.800
What is it like to be Brazilian?

2
00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.000
It's to have the ability to overcome situations.

3
00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:08.300
To get out of the crisis as new nation.

4
00:00:08.400 --> 00:00:13.600
It's to cross new borders and build dreams of a lifetime.

5
00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:19.400
What is it be Brazilian? It's to work hard and still live lightly.

6
00:00:19.600 --> 00:00:22.700
To keep the mood yet being determinated.

7
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
Enter the field to take victory home.

8
00:00:26.100 --> 00:00:28.100
Show potential to go even deeper.

9
00:00:28.200 --> 00:00:31.000
To have a solid base industry.

10
00:00:31.200 --> 00:00:34.000
Create planes that fly overseas.

11
00:00:34.200 --> 00:00:36.000
To be an entrepreneur by nature.

12
00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:39.700
To take a piece of Brazil to every table.

13
00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:42.000
To be seen with new eyes.

14
00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:45.100
Eyes of those who work hard and deserve consideration.

15
00:00:45.200 --> 00:00:48.700
We create, transform, make it right.

16
00:00:49.000 --> 00:00:54.000
Being Brazilian, that's our way.

17
00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:00.000
We are living a new Brazil, made by you. Brazil, a country of all.


